node.text: Teaching is hard. Really hard. Sundays can be especially stressful as educators gear up for the week. The purpose of the Stress Less Sunday for Educators series will be to help educators be in the best mental space possible for the upcoming week!

Photo by TeacherGoals on July 23, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of one or more people and text that says '10 Lessons I Want to Instill in My Kids... If you're thankful, show it. If you love someone, tell them. If you're wrong, fess up. If you're confused, ask questions. If you learn something, teach others. If you're stuck, ask for help. If you made a mistake, apologize. If you trip, get back up. If someone needs help, help them. If you see wrong, take a stance.'.
